      <title>波兰拖延向前执政党发放资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/poland-drags-heels-on-releasing-funds-to-former-ruling-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰财政部长选择推迟向前执政的民族主义政党发放有争议的政府资金，这有可能在该国总统大选前引发进一步的政治动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/poland-drags-heels-on-releasing-funds-to-former-ruling-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 20:06:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普威胁升级，加拿大首席执行官呼吁提前选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/some-ceos-want-emergency-election-in-canada-as-trump-escalates-his-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普不断升级的关税威胁以及他吞并加拿大的言论，促使一些加拿大商界领袖呼吁立即开展竞选活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/some-ceos-want-emergency-election-in-canada-as-trump-escalates-his-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 19:58:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰总统在奥斯维辛解放活动中寻求对内塔尼亚胡的保护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/polish-president-seeks-protection-for-netanyahu-at-auschwitz-liberation-event</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总统要求政府保护本雅明内塔尼亚胡，以免他在以色列总理出席该国举行的奥斯维辛解放 80 周年纪念活动时被捕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/polish-president-seeks-protection-for-netanyahu-at-auschwitz-liberation-event</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 19:45:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国保守党未能迫使斯塔默对强奸团伙展开调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/uk-tories-fail-in-bid-to-force-starmer-to-hold-rape-gang-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国反对党保守党曾试图迫使首相基尔·斯塔默对所谓的儿童性侵团伙丑闻展开全国调查，但未能成功。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/uk-tories-fail-in-bid-to-force-starmer-to-hold-rape-gang-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 19:22:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国专家称，刚果伊斯兰叛乱分子大开杀戒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/islamist-rebels-on-record-killing-spree-in-congo-un-experts-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国专家周三表示，6 月至 11 月初，一支与伊斯兰国有联系的伊斯兰民兵组织在刚果民主共和国杀害了 650 多名平民，这是该组织有史以来最致命的行动之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/islamist-rebels-on-record-killing-spree-in-congo-un-experts-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 18:51:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布林肯拒绝特朗普夺取格陵兰岛，称“这不会发生”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/blinken-rejects-a-trump-greenland-grab-as-not-going-to-happen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周三在巴黎表示，尽管当选总统唐纳德·特朗普发表了好战的言论，但美国永远不会接管格陵兰岛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/blinken-rejects-a-trump-greenland-grab-as-not-going-to-happen</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 18:47:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
